    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0316">
<l>ilameṉ kiḷavikkup paṭuvaru kālai</l>
<l>nilaiyalu murittē ceyyu ḷāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilam</foreign> ' poverty ' is followed by <foreign xml:lang="ta">paṭu</foreign> ' to experience ',</l>
<l>it may remain, in poetry.<note place="foot">i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilam + pāṭu &gt; ilampāṭu</foreign> ' to become poor, to suffer poverty '. Cf. Malai-paṭukaṭam 576, <foreign xml:lang="ta">ilampaṭu pulavar.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
